dcterms:description: The MNIST dataset consists of 70,000 images of handwritten digits, with 60,000 for training and 10,000 for testing. It is widely used for benchmarking machine learning algorithms.
dcterms:title: MNIST

dcterms:creator: H. Xiao

dcterms:description: Fashion MNIST is a dataset of 70,000 grayscale images of clothing items, with 60,000 for training and 10,000 for testing. It serves as a drop-in replacement for the MNIST dataset for benchmarking machine learning algorithms.
dcterms:title: Fashion MNIST
